Create the file /Users/charlesvictormahouve/Documents/GitHub/africandatalayer/components/SyncStatusBar.tsx

This is a persistent sync status bar that replaces the offline-only amber banner. It shows on all screens except Splash and Auth.

Requirements:
- 28dp height (h-7), sticky below header, does not scroll with content
- 4 states based on props:
  1. All synced (online, 0 pending, 0 failed): Green dot, subtle text "X synced", refresh icon
  2. Syncing (isSyncing=true): Animated spinner, "Syncing..." text
  3. Offline + pending (isOffline=true, pending > 0): Amber background, "HORS LIGNE - X en attente" / "OFFLINE - X pending"
  4. Failed submissions (failed > 0): Red background, "X echecs - Appuyez pour voir" / "X failed - Tap to view"
- Tapping the bar calls onTap callback (will open SubmissionQueue)
- Refresh icon button calls onRefresh callback
- Uses lucide-react icons: RefreshCw, Wifi, WifiOff, AlertCircle, CheckCircle
- Bilingual EN/FR via language prop
- Props interface:
  ```
  interface Props {
    pending: number;
    failed: number;
    synced: number;
    isOffline: boolean;
    isSyncing: boolean;
    onTap?: () => void;
    onRefresh?: () => void;
    language: 'en' | 'fr';
  }
  ```

Style: Use Tailwind classes consistent with the existing app. Brand colors: navy #0f2b46, success green #4c7c59, warning amber, error red #c53030. Text should be text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest (matching the existing offline banner pattern).

Write the complete component file.

